{"tid":248891,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"摩氏曼聯創英超單賽季最少勝仗紀錄","createTime":"2017-05-19T02:12:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-19T04:22:20.000Z","uid":3806,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"320f765194f72d4dd402665311ee87362deea012","tid":248891,"uid":3806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T02:12:52.000Z","msg":"在今天凌晨的一場補賽當中，曼聯與修咸頓握手言和，雖然比賽結果已經無關痛癢，但還是讓曼聯創造了新紀錄。<br />\n<img src=\"http://n2.hk/d/attachments/day_170518/20170518_4dcaa8da45d39bf0e7d8cl0wTAKwBeis.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fn2.hk%2Fd%2Fattachments%2Fday_170518%2F20170518_4dcaa8da45d39bf0e7d8cl0wTAKwBeis.jpg&h=7e0b3ae9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n平局過多是曼聯本賽季表現不佳的一大原因，本場比賽是紅魔本賽季的第15場平局，已經創造了球隊在英超時代的最多平局紀錄；上一次曼聯平局較多的賽季是在1998-99賽季，當時曼聯打平了13場比賽，但是贏得了22場比賽，最終拿到了當賽季的英超冠軍。<br />\n<br />\n此外，本場比賽也是曼聯本賽季的第6場0-0，此前發生這種情況還是在2004-05賽季，凸顯了球隊進攻火力的不足。<br />\n<img src=\"http://n2.hk/d/attachments/day_170518/20170518_ce3cca011ad5617efff3H0b3XZZhHpXt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fn2.hk%2Fd%2Fattachments%2Fday_170518%2F20170518_ce3cca011ad5617efff3H0b3XZZhHpXt.jpg&h=663cc41e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n到目前為止，曼聯只贏下了17場比賽，同樣也將刷新球會單賽季聯賽最少勝場紀錄，即使最後一輪取勝，摩連奴的球隊也只是取勝18場，而此前的最低紀錄是上賽季的19場勝利。"},{"pid":"a335915a3e5d2de7fdc5632de282362d40d41c88","tid":248891,"uid":3806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T02:13:43.000Z","msg":"摩氏皇朝屢破紀錄<br />\nDaddy is the king of England !!!<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J283uc.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ283uc.gif&h=8894c724&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"48a212841ff85491e0e1ae82c2c5782beeeb7bd6","tid":248891,"uid":3806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T02:14:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/I/618kHlQNvkL._UX385_.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-na.ssl-images-amazon.com%2Fimages%2FI%2F618kHlQNvkL._UX385_.jpg&h=2492a5df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n送對襪俾你打 J ，慶祝埋車仔奪冠啦唉"},{"pid":"a312892465232a543377a5e9e97635be10e68832","tid":248891,"uid":91875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T02:14:38.000Z","msg":"人力留力歐霸,留力歐超,留力下年聯賽,留力.......<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> V92 is innocent"},{"pid":"0d40cf1f2b668df8eacf4dd1b9aa3c60d7cb237d","tid":248891,"uid":37735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T02:15:28.000Z","msg":"椰子無水喉 44%<br />\n摩佬有水喉 37.5%<br />\n見曼post椰子年代 屌 咩搞度主場霸氣不再 <br />\n<br />\n椰子是無辜的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a63b00e1c60945d2d01bc09e30c3c44a9eb4f104","tid":248891,"uid":91875,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T02:16:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>椰子無水喉 44%<br />\n摩佬有水喉 37.5%<br />\n見曼post椰子年代 屌 咩搞度主場霸氣不再 <br />\n<br />\n椰子是無辜的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n雲高爾洗錢成績都好過摩狗"},{"pid":"02e0e8d52c8ae33aa5150010a7e87e0d5338e750","tid":248891,"uid":37735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T02:18:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>椰子無水喉 44%<br />\n摩佬有水喉 37.5%<br />\n見曼post椰子年代 屌 咩搞度主場霸氣不再 <br />\n<br />\n椰子是無辜的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n教曼仲要教到心靈創傷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無左拖肥果陣實力"},{"pid":"813385ec279c79bd011ac3a8090aa2250c7f7768","tid":248891,"uid":91875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T02:20:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>椰子無水喉 44%<br />\n摩佬有水喉 37.5%<br />\n見曼post椰子年代 屌 咩搞度主場霸氣不再 <br />\n<br />\n椰子是無辜的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n教曼仲要教到心靈創傷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"h